headline: Citi says a ‘supermajors super-cycle’ is coming for U.S. airlines
summary: Investing.com -- Citi analyst John Godyn said in a note Thursday that the U.S. airline industry is heading into what they call a “Supermajors Super-Cycle,” arguing that 2026 will mark the start of an elongated mid-cycle in which the largest network carriers outperform the rest of the sector.

headline: Dow Jones Futures Rise; Snowflake Melts On Outlook After Tesla, Robinhood Lead Broad Rally
summary: The market rallied broadly Wednesday, with bullish Tesla and Robinhood moves. Snowflake fell overnight on its earnings outlook.
